title: 5 Best Android Apps not Available on Google Play [Part 3]
tags: Android Apps not Available on Google Play Store
description:
Download links of Apps, I've used in this video, can be found on my blog -- https://goo.gl/RcaiYI

Wallpaper link https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1sqEWrNRx0xa3lEV3pPdzJ1QlU/view?usp=docslist_api

Here is the third part of 5 Android apps not available on Google Play. 

#1 TinyTunes stream or download music like you do in Netease, but comes in English interface. 

#2 FrostWire a torrent client which also lets you download videos, music, images etc. It's similar to Media river, but with a huge database.

#3 SCR pro a free screen recorder app for Android that records audio from both internal/external speaker and also has a face cam. May or may not require root depending on your Android version and hardware. 

#4 MovieHD/CartoonHD stream movies and tv shows on your Android or cast it on the chromecast. A good alternative to Showbox and tv portal. 

#5 zANTI [root] advance WiFi penetration toolkit that you can use to see what people are browsing/downloading on your network. It also has SSL strip to change https sites to open as http instead.
